{"id":835,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":835,"title":"Ezekiel 7","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 7"],[".studySummary",["i","Desolation, war, pestilence, and destruction will sweep the land of Israel—The desolation of the people is foreseen."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.1","order":"02.27.007.55324"},["b","1"],"Moreover the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.2","order":"02.27.007.55325"},["b","2"],"Also, thou son of man, thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"unto the land of Israel; An",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"end"],", the end is come upon the four corners of the land."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.3","order":"02.27.007.55326"},["b","3"],"Now",["i","is"],"the end",["i","come"],"upon thee, and I will send mine anger upon thee, and will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"judge"],"thee according to thy ways, and will recompense upon thee all thine abominations."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.4","order":"02.27.007.55327"},["b","4"],"And mine eye shall not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"spare"],"thee, neither will I have pity: but I will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"recompense"],"thy ways upon thee, and thine abominations shall be in the midst of thee: and ye shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"know"],"that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.5","order":"02.27.007.55328"},["b","5"],"Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; An evil, an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"only"],"evil, behold, is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"come"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.6","order":"02.27.007.55329"},["b","6"],"An end is come, the end is come: it watcheth for thee; behold, it is come."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.7","order":"02.27.007.55330"},["b","7"],"The morning is come unto thee, O thou that dwellest in the land: the time is come, the day of trouble",["i","is"],"near, and not the sounding again of the mountains."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.8","order":"02.27.007.55331"},["b","8"],"Now will I shortly pour out my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"fury"],"upon thee, and accomplish mine anger upon thee: and I will judge thee according to thy ways, and will recompense thee for all thine abominations."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.9","order":"02.27.007.55332"},["b","9"],"And mine eye shall not spare, neither will I have pity: I will recompense thee according to thy ways and thine abominations",["i","that"],"are in the midst of thee; and ye shall know that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"that smiteth."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.10","order":"02.27.007.55333"},["b","10"],"Behold the day, behold, it is come: the morning is gone forth; the rod hath blossomed, pride hath budded."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.11","order":"02.27.007.55334"},["b","11"],"Violence is risen up into a rod of wickedness: none of them",["i","shall remain,"],"nor of their multitude, nor of any of theirs: neither",["i","shall there be"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"wailing"],"for them."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.12","order":"02.27.007.55335"},["b","12"],"The time is come, the day draweth near: let not the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"buyer"],"rejoice, nor the seller mourn: for wrath",["i","is"],"upon all the multitude thereof."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.13","order":"02.27.007.55336"},["b","13"],"For the seller shall not return to that which is sold, although they were yet alive: for the vision",["i","is"],"touching the whole multitude thereof,",["i","which"],"shall not return; neither shall any strengthen himself in the iniquity of his life."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.14","order":"02.27.007.55337"},["b","14"],"They have blown the trumpet, even to make all ready; but none goeth to the battle: for my wrath",["i","is"],"upon all the multitude thereof."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.15","order":"02.27.007.55338"},["b","15"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"sword"],["i","is"],"without, and the pestilence and the famine within: he that",["i","is"],"in the field shall die with the sword; and he that",["i","is"],"in the city, famine and pestilence shall devour him."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.16","order":"02.27.007.55339"},["b","16"],"¶But they that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"escape"],"of them shall escape, and shall be on the mountains like doves of the valleys, all of them",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"mourning"],", every one for his iniquity."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.17","order":"02.27.007.55340"},["b","17"],"All",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"hands"],"shall be feeble, and all knees shall be weak",["i","as"],"water."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.18","order":"02.27.007.55341"},["b","18"],"They shall also gird",["i","themselves"],"with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"sackcloth"],", and horror shall cover them; and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"shame"],["i","shall be"],"upon all faces, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"baldness"],"upon all their heads."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.19","order":"02.27.007.55342"},["b","19"],"They shall cast their silver in the streets, and their gold shall be removed: their silver and their gold shall not be able to deliver them in the day of the wrath of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": they shall not satisfy their souls, neither fill their bowels: because it is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"stumblingblock"],"of their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"iniquity"],"."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.20","order":"02.27.007.55343"},["b","20"],"¶As for the beauty of his ornament, he set it in majesty: but they made the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"images"],"of their abominations",["i","and"],"of their detestable things therein: therefore have I set it far from them."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.21","order":"02.27.007.55344"},["b","21"],"And I will give it into the hands of the strangers for a prey, and to the wicked of the earth for a spoil; and they shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"pollute"],"it."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.22","order":"02.27.007.55345"},["b","22"],"My face will I turn also from them, and they shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"pollute"],"my secret",["i",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"place"],":"],"for the robbers shall enter into it, and defile it."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.23","order":"02.27.007.55346"},["b","23"],"¶Make a chain: for the land is full of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"bloody crimes"],", and the city is full of violence."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.24","order":"02.27.007.55347"},["b","24"],"Wherefore I will bring the worst of the heathen, and they shall possess their houses: I will also make the pomp of the strong to cease; and their holy places shall be defiled."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.25","order":"02.27.007.55348"},["b","25"],"Destruction cometh; and they shall seek peace, and",["i","there shall be"],"none."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.26","order":"02.27.007.55349"},["b","26"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"Mischief"],"shall come upon mischief, and rumour shall be upon rumour; then shall they seek a vision of the prophet; but the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"law"],"shall perish from the priest, and counsel from the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_26c"},"ancients"],"."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.27","order":"02.27.007.55350"},["b","27"],"The king shall mourn, and the prince shall be clothed with desolation, and the hands of the people of the land shall be troubled: I will do unto them after their way, and according to their deserts will I judge them; and they shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"know"],"that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.2a","order":"02.27.007.55351"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.18"},"Lam. 4:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/8.2"},"Amos 8:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.3a","order":"02.27.007.55353"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.13"},"1 Sam. 3:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.30"},"Ezek. 18:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.4a","order":"02.27.007.55355"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.11"},"Ezek. 5:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.4b","order":"02.27.007.55357"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/9.10"},"Ezek. 9:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/11.21"},"11:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/16.43"},"16:43"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/22.31"},"22:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.10"},"D&C 1:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.4c","order":"02.27.007.55359"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-knowledge-about"},"TG God, Knowledge about"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.5a","order":"02.27.007.55361"},["b","5a"],["span.small","OR"],"singular or unique."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.5b","order":"02.27.007.55363"},["b","5b"],["span.small","OR"],"coming."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.8a","order":"02.27.007.55365"},["b","8a"],["a.s